{"tid":1052311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連匪完全瓦解咗高登文法！！即係瓦解香港網絡文化","createTime":"2019-03-08T08:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T13:48:39.000Z","uid":58335,"like":204,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a313035f63af89f5e829da3ff102406a66a43220","tid":1052311,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"連登當初成立(奪權)目的就係為左代替高登<br />\n但以前啲高登文化<br />\n好似潮文，專用名詞而家已經慢慢變到冇人識<br />\n<br />\n雖然一個壇有佢自己既文化係好事<br />\n但可惜匪登唔係有自己文化<br />\n而係不繼引入5p文化，交配小圈子，甚至大劣文化都有<br />\n仲有大把返大陸飲食po<br />\n以前打5p字比人屌到仆街<br />\n而家班mk屌返你轉頭<br />\n劣幣驅逐良幣<br />\n<br />\n當高登文化消失<br />\n冇另一套優質文化頂上<br />\n就會做成思想真空<br />\n情況同共匪消滅華夏文化一樣<br />\n又如共匪對香港文化清洗<br />\n<br />\n消滅左香港網絡文化<br />\n所以而家啲00後就係到666，牛b死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連匪真係亡港之人"},{"pid":"88866812ebcb1d8df4166ba44f93767b34367aa1","tid":1052311,"uid":99607,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:17:59.000Z","msg":"連登係明<br />\n高登在暗"},{"pid":"7320c9b0fefbd50982037ed0080d1545f9a90cf7","tid":1052311,"uid":196924,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"咩叫不繼引入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪想講不斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ae8df52eb1c7f0d2fc859951923d4123c6e2d3","tid":1052311,"uid":21423,"like":16,"dislike":9,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e5685cf4f33bdfbaa08636f5cf4c0346b6a12e4","tid":1052311,"uid":49812,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88866812ebcb1d8df4166ba44f93767b34367aa1","tid":1052311,"uid":99607,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:17:59.000Z","msg":"連登係明<br />\n高登在暗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:20:54.000Z","msg":"你講緊奶共姿態？<br />\n連登可能同腥講01有關係添"},{"pid":"a980ea082917517555cbca23815305820badd440","tid":1052311,"uid":27766,"like":9,"dislike":2,"scor