" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd 藍波撚 想講其他體育o既新會然我地刀趕走晒啦 但賭波撚本是一家 不分你我gama<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對不對 再吾系 我地返joe囝度la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1746c8d7f9acfb42305c9727c15e5d839234c092","tid":1052311,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登潮文</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/206646/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/206646/page/1</a><br />\n我都知道好多好鍾意足球嘅小朋友嚟到呢個險惡邪惡黑暗嘅時事台之後，唔識返屋企。所以就驚到喺度唔知點做，所以喺度瘋狂開足球post，希望可以召集一班同道中人返屋企。我都知道你哋好返去，可能你哋唔識返去。等哥哥教下你啦! 首先係呢部電話嘅左方，用手指向右拉出。<br />\n然後喺咁多嘅台， 逐個逐個慢慢睇。 之後就會見到體育台架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天黑喇大家快啲返屋企啦，你啲屋企人好擔心你地架。 可能會報警叫人出嚟搵你地架。<br />\n快啲返屋企啦夜晚可能冇車架啦⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a06261ce81d122e3c8e4398d9b2e0804d76d6cc","tid":1052311,"uid":191926,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4064602b1173cfc01ccbd38559bb768ca2de3216","tid":1052311,"uid":74935,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"瓦解高登明明就係呀joe<br />\n唔係佢點會有連登出現<br />\n倒轉晒啲嘢嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"3個原因<br />\n<br />\n1. 草泥馬的舊仇<br />\n女夜鬼等引起出走事件 已經搞左幾次<br />\n好多高登仔都有少少離心<br />\n包捨中間派<br />\n<br />\n2.科技落後<br />\n<br />\n草泥馬話高登因為連尼住 所以慢<br />\n根本有少少年資都知<br />\n10年前都好撚柒慢  如果星期六，日晚踢緊足球果陣   因為大量人reload<br />\n成個forum 慢到  一分鐘先f5到一次<br />\n<br />\n3. 4年前區議會選舉<br />\n熱狗為左搶話語權  攻擊其他政見人士<br />\n最癲果彈  時事台，吹水台 <br />\n一係就開post屌唔知邊個 <br />\n一係就成班係度吹噓果個 <br />\n(好像鄭錦滿好撚真心)"},{"pid":"f01588836decbdf072b6c0b14e24f571503d0890","tid":1052311,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:52:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/1</a><br />\n你地今年拎唔到西甲冠軍，俾你地戀棧最近八年歷史都算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何必詛咒皇空難死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講番今晚場波，俾啲掌聲先啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學陸運會指定動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天天天，你地聲震天。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地地地，雖然你地打毗係贏左我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地聲震天，你地打毗又贏左我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我地攞冠軍，我皇冠軍已袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n贏我地，又如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/7?ref=web&amp;post=160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/7?ref=web&amp;post=160</a><br />\nEvery day, you sounding the sky.<br />\nTo ground, although you fight to match the left to win me.<br />\nYou sound the sound of the earth, you play to win and left me.<br />\nBut I have to champion, my crown has bags<br />\nWin me and how<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/7?ref=web&amp;post=166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/7?ref=web&amp;post=166</a><br />\n毎日、あなたの雷の音に。<br />\n地面、あなたが勝つために左の境界線に私を襲ったが。<br />\nあなたが耳をつんざくようなことが、あなたは左の境界と勝利に私を襲いました。<br />\nしかし、私は羅選手権に、私は袋に帝国のタイトルを持っています<br />\n私は勝つために持っている、そしてどのように<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/9?ref=web&amp;post=213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/9?ref=web&amp;post=213</a><br />\n天天天，爾等聲震天。<br />\n地地地，雖爾等競是勝過吾等。<br />\n爾等聲震天，爾等競復勝過吾等。<br />\n僅吾等得冠，吾皇冠已落囊。<br />\n勝吾等，復何哉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/10?ref=web&amp;post=246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/252762/page/10?ref=web&amp;post=246</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/172259_9e190b907debcd2a9b91e77fb525c5bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F172259_9e190b907debcd2a9b91e77fb525c5bf.jpg&h=2f4ca06d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/172303_caf8ffc24df84f97bd8bb7f9c8d271ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F172303_caf8ffc24df84f97bd8bb7f9c8d271ad.jpg&h=38f455ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/172305_ce438c90f5bc2aab0096a5f409dc6fdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F172305_ce438c90f5bc2aab0096a5f409dc6fdf.jpg&h=7da218ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/172308_9a0dfa59525e778e9994028cea1912c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F172308_9a0dfa59525e778e9994028cea1912c5.jpg&h=8c11d097&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1a9c40b41f105d46543d899c7d195e75572df5b","tid":1052311,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6627a5b36a7bd14cb5410bf6bbdea464f19ee4bb","tid":1052311,"uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"所以，要眾籌，搞個新論壇，去紅色資本<br />\n<br />\n提升本土意識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"用.onion網域嚟開"},{"pid":"0b8ea48dad2571ed8736046803cd91fdaa1d2d51","tid":1052311,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">連登潮文</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/277704/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/277704/page/2</a><br />\n女人...<br />\n<br />\n有前戲就叫你唔好搞咁多嘢,催你帶套<br />\n冇前戲又話鳩你咁趕咁猴擒做乜<br />\n唔掂佢又問你係咪出面同第條女搞完嚟,仲要扮撚晒委屈咁問你係咪唔愛佢<br />\n你一下唔為意發咗吓脾氣,就連頭髮都唔使旨意掂到,出廳瞓啦*M 你!<br />\n<br />\n好喇,當你有得被恩准有前戲,又有百鳩幾個問題出現喇,<br />\n除佢衫又話熱/凍 摸下個胸就問你做乜一嚟就揸波 摸下面又話唔鍾意<br />\n隔手夾腳呢啲嘢在所難免 未埋牙就已經好似打完詠春咁攰<br />\n唔單止鬥力,仲要鬥智 你摸佢個胸時讚下佢大波好正,佢會無啦啦問你&ldquo;如果有第條女個胸大過我你又會上啦?&rdquo; 喂大佬呢啲問題都問得出口,唔通我真係答會咩。到你答唔會佢又話你假,之後擰撚轉身唔比搞。 含撚,舔身呢啲嘢根本唔使諗,就算你副軀殼有幾乾淨都有問題。<br />\n唔洗乾淨有異味唔含唔舔好正常,人人都會 洗乾淨都被嫌棄有陣梘液味,到底前世做錯啲咩先會溝到件咁嘅女。<br />\n<br />\n縱使你已經身心俱疲,但又當你再過一關,準備埋牙,問題又出現喇!<br />\n如果冇前戲條女下面唔濕,咁你就咁入佢當然會痛啦,但你又唔可以用手/口接觸到佢下面,咁點算呢?唯有用念力希望佢自動出水,又或者實際啲,用啲有多啲潤滑劑嘅condom囉。 入撚到你就以為會見到曙光好撚巴閉,非也。所有一舉一動都要被支配住,用力少少就話大力,細力啲又問你係咪冇食飯,轉體位又話 好地地做乜要轉,唔轉位又話同一個位唔有趣,試吓新體位又問你邊度學返嚟(下刪訓話x2046)。撞啱有日狀態好啲,持久咗,都要比條 女屈係咪之前射咗Q。<br />\n算喇乜心情都冇晒,投降唔做,條女隻委屈鬼又上身,話你唔尊重佢 唔愛佢,衰啲嘅連馬尿都標埋。好嘢,又要好似氹細路咁氹返佢,之 後比佢責撚住對手瞓成晚,第朝隻手郁唔撚到。<br />\n<br />\n總之同屋企嗰個做愛,仲辛苦過返工。"},{"pid":"b485dd323c44e4b050ec73bc2996a7c0c6536fe8","tid":1052311,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"連登其實係由高登愛國波台支+DISCUSS/UWANT愛國份子+交配5P仔+政府冷感,窮到只係淘寶SHOPPING涯日子既親子王國C奶組成"},{"pid":"75b4285f46242f1314be5e1624e8aef272e0f805","tid":1052311,"uid":31637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"高登文化的確冇撚晒<br />\n<br />\n得返D開POST話你抄晒車既傻仔"},{"pid":"8a640d61aaa6eb28b0775851e7ccb53958b1270a","tid":1052311,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b485dd323c44e4b050ec73bc2996a7c0c6536fe8","tid":1052311,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"連登其實係由高登愛國波台支+DISCUSS/UWANT愛國份子+交配5P仔+政府冷感,窮到只係淘寶SHOPPING涯日子既親子王國C奶組成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"一矢中的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24729708971413cc4f63d807a389a258f2fb0833","tid":1052311,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1a9c40b41f105d46543d899c7d195e75572df5b","tid":1052311,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6627a5b36a7bd14cb5410bf6bbdea464f19ee4bb","tid":1052311,"uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"所以，要眾籌，搞個新論壇，去紅色資本<br />\n<br />\n提升本土意識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"用.onion網域嚟開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:21:32.000Z","msg":"咁即係一般人唔使上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d62e04bb1b22f9541ef33249365c9a557983de3","tid":1052311,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b485dd323c44e4b050ec73bc2996a7c0c6536fe8","tid":1052311,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"連登其實係由高登愛國波台支+DISCUSS/UWANT愛國份子+交配5P仔+政府冷感,窮到只係淘寶SHOPPING涯日子既親子王國C奶組成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:23:01.000Z","msg":"的確